Class Gambler

  • java.lang.Object
    • player.Player
      • player.Gambler

  • public class Gambler
extends Player
    The Gambler Class inherits from Player. It adds the functionality of betting and allowing the user to decide whether to hit or stand.
    Author:
    RossWeinstein
